Osiem jo-Israel kuom lamo nyiseche manono


1  Ruoth Nyasaye wacho niya, “Go tung’, nikech wasigu yako Hekalu mara, mana ka otenga mayudho nyagweno! Joga oseketho singruok mane atimo kodgi, kendo gisedagi winjo puonjna. 
2  Kata obedo ni giluonga ni Nyasachgi kendo giwacho ni ging’eya kamano, 
3  to gisedagi gima ber, mano omiyo wasikgi biro lawogi. 
4  Joga yiero ruodhi maggi, to gitimo kamano ma ok gipenja. Bende giyiero jotelo ka ok ayie. Gikawo fedha gi dhahabu ma gin-go, kendo giloso nyiseche manono ma biro kelonigi mana masira. 
5  Asedagi nyaroya mar dhahabu ma jo-Samaria lamo, kendo mirimba ng’ang’ni kuomgi. Koro pod gidwaro ni mondo akumgi nyaka karang’o? 
6  Jatich moro e Israel ema ne oloso kido manono, to kidono ok en Nyasaye! Kido mar nyaroya ma jo-Samaria lamono ibiro baro matindo tindo.


7  “Jo-Israel chwoyo yamo, to gikayo mana kalausi. Gin gi cham ma ok wuodhi, omiyo gionge gi mogo. To kapo ni onyago cham, to jopinje mamoko dichame, mi tieke. 
8  Jo-Israel duto ibiro mwonyo, mi tieki pep. To kata mana sani ogendini mamoko okawogi ka joma nono. 
9  Gisedhi Asuria mondo giyudie konyruok, ka gichalo kanj thim moringo oa e kweth, kendo gitimo mana gima gin ema gidwaro. Adier, jo-Israel oseng’iewore kuom ogendini mamoko mondo okonygi. 
10  To koro abiro chokogi mondo akumgi! Piyopiyo nono gibiro neno malit ka ruodh Asuria sandogi.


11  “Kaka jo-Israel medo kende-mag-misango mang’eny mondo ogolgo richo e kaka gimedo bedo gi kuonde mang’eny ma gitimoe richo. 
12  Andiko chike gana gi gana mondo ji opuonjre, to gidagi ni mago gik mayore yore ma ok ging’eyo. 
13  Gihero timo misengni, kendo gihero chamo ring misengnigo. To an Ruoth Nyasaye ok amor kodgi, kendo abiro paro richogi mi akumgi, ka adwokogi e piny Misri. 
14  Jo-Israel osegero ut ruodhi, to wigi owil gi jachuechgi. Jo-Juda osegero mier mochiel motegno, to abiro oro mach mondo owang’ miego kaachiel gi ut ruodhigo.”

